name: sillytavern-namegen-extension
description: SillyTavern extension for generating names using fantastical

scripts.fetch:fantastical: mkdir -p lib && npx --yes download-cli https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fantastical@2.0.1/dist/index.js lib/fantastical.js || curl -fsSL https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fantastical@2.0.1/dist/index.js -o lib/fantastical.js
